---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Contact · ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="How to get in touch with the Optimist Club of Mount Horeb, Wisconsin — Facebook, email, and where to find us in person." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>

			<!-- Hello -->
			<section class="bg-white">
				<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-optimist-blue">Contact</h1>
					<p class="mt-10 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-optimist-blue">
						Hello. We're glad you're here. Whatever brought you to this page &mdash; a question, an idea, or just curiosity about who we are &mdash; thanks for spending a minute of your day with us.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Ways to reach us -->
			<section class="bg-optimist-beige">
				<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
					<div class="space-y-12 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-optimist-blue">

						<div>
							<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-optimist-blue mb-4">Facebook</h2>
							<p>
								We have a <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mounthoreboptimistclub" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Facebook page</a> we're genuinely proud of. We've been at it for years &mdash; long before this website existed &mdash; and there's a lot there: photos from events, the people, the projects, the small stuff that doesn't make it onto a webpage. If you want to see what the club actually looks like in motion, that's the place. Come find us there.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div>
							<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-optimist-blue mb-4">Email</h2>
							<p>
								If you have a question, an idea, or anything you want to put in front of the club, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@mounthoreboptimist.com" class="underline">hello@mounthoreboptimist.com</a>. Whatever it is, we'll get it to the right person and someone will get back to you.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div>
							<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-optimist-blue mb-4">Come see us</h2>
							<p>
								You'll find us all over the village throughout the year &mdash; wherever there's something good happening for the kids of Mount Horeb, we try to be there. But our home base is the Mount Horeb Public Library, third Monday of every month. If you'd rather just meet us in person, that's where to find us.
							</p>
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Closing + photo note -->
			<section class="bg-white">
				<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-optimist-blue">
						Mount Horeb is, by nature, an optimistic village &mdash; and we're grateful our club gets to serve that optimism in our own small way, one smile at a time, with the kids at the center of it all. Thanks for visiting our website; you're someone we'd like to meet.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-16 text-sm leading-relaxed text-optimist-blue/70">
						We try to be thoughtful about the photos we share here and on Facebook &mdash; most are from public events, and we're proud of the moments they capture. If you or your child appear in a photo on this site and you'd rather not, please write to us at <a href="mailto:mounthoreboptimist@gmail.com" class="underline">mounthoreboptimist@gmail.com</a> and we'll take it down. No explanation needed.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
